Gaupol 0.17
===========

 [D] Add "Save All As" (under the Projects menu) to save all open
     documents with selected properties (fixes #595685)
 [D] Add an inline spell-check for editable multiline text fields (off
     by default, can be activated in the preferences dialog)
 [D] Add support for milliseconds (field $MILLISECONDS) in preview
     commands (allows use of Media Player Classic for preview)
 [D] Add help button in the preferences dialog, clickable in the
     preview tab to launch web browser to view wiki documentation
 [D] Add optional dependency of PyGtkSpell (part of
     gnome-python-extras)
 [D] Fix minor i18n issues with individual strings
 [D] Add --mandir global option to setup.py (fixes #620665)
 [D] Add Finnish translation

 [ ] Fix problems with extension configurations

Gaupol 1.0
==========

 * Add a built-in GStreamer-based video player

